## EcoXchange guardrails

- Develop on the assigned feature branch; do not push to `main` without explicit approval.
- Do not edit files inside `.claude/skills/gstack/` — that is an upstream submodule.
- For `cso`: prioritize Persona / OpenAI / Solcast keys, the Securitize mock-vs-real boundary, and the public `/api/public/backtest/*` surface.
- For `qa` / `health`: golden paths are `/performance` and `/backtest-report`; do not regress the SCADA CSV upload at `/operations`.
